    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s specimen, maintained with obsessive care since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish thanks to a professional multi-stage ceramic coating, with absolutely zero stone chips, swirls, or door dings to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather retains its original matte texture and fresh scent, with no visible wear on the driver\u2019s side bolsters, steering wheel, or touchpoints. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive binder of every service record included. Always garage-kept under a breathable cover and never driven in inclement weather, this car performs with the precision and tightness of a brand-new vehicle. It comes complete with all original keys, factory manuals, and a clean title in hand for a seamless transition to its next steward.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
