      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably maintained vehicle, an asset that truly defines showroom excellence. Every aspect of this automobile\u2014from its flawless exterior finish to the pristine condition of its interior appointments\u2014has been preserved with exacting standards. This vehicle has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous criteria for mechanical and aesthetic perfection. For the collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than an unblemished driving experience, this offering stands as a premier example of automotive preservation.",
      "price": 48500.0,
